<db:section xml:id="the-qml-preview">
<db:title>The Qml Preview</db:title>
<db:para>The QML Preview tool watches QML and JavaScript files on disk and updates the application live with any changes. The application to be previewed has to have QML debugging enabled. <db:link xlink:href="qtqml-tooling-qmlpreview.xml#enable-qml-debugging">More...</db:link></db:para>
